data.description: Welcome to your new oasis! This 3-bed, 2-bath gem is all about easy living.  This home includes an inviting island kitchen with sleek appliances. Picture yourself entertaining in the open-concept living and dining areas, flooded with natural light. The three cozy bedrooms and stylish bathrooms complete the package. This home is not just a house; it's a warm haven waiting for you! Convenient to highway, Brooks City Base, and shopping.
